metadata.name: Moon Money: Cyborg Collection #1
metadata.description:
“Moon Money: Cyborg Collection” featuring Mark Zuckerberg. Each NFT is 1 of 55.

“Moon Money” is a series of eight (8) NFT collections. Each of the collections is a unique fictional currency, featuring a different historical figure. The NFT currencies are political parody, that include binary and hex code, creating a historical record related to the individual featured. Translate the code to learn more. 

Creative Director Billie Halliday. Illustrations by Igor Bratchyn.
